  "claim_short": "The packet gives an explicit real Fourier-mode orthonormal basis for the cocycle Hilbert space associated with the odd-cycle word length on Z_{2m+1}^n. The basis also shows that the coordinate subspaces are invariant under the cocycle action, that the coordinate support derivatives partial_j lambda(g) = 1_{g_j != 0} lambda(g) are distinguished, and therefore that the same balanced Fourier-truncation X_p inequality...",
